Jacobson Stores Inc said itsboard voted a three-for-two stock split, payble March 30,record March 13.    In other action, Jacobson's directors approved an increasein its quarterly dividend to 11 cts on a post split basispayable April 14, record March 30.    The new dividend rate represents a 32 pct increase over the12-1/2 cts paid quarterly on a pre-split basis. Reuter&#3;